	    });

		    e.stopPropagation();

		    var handler = $(this).prop('onclick');

		    $(this).click(handler);
		});
	});

<script>
function shortenedUrl()
{
if( $('.smsm.lnIco .linkBox') .is(":visible") == true) {
//  console.log('shorter visible now will be hide');
  $('.smsm.lnIco .linkBox').hide();
} else {
  var url = window.location.toString();
  var azuid=0;
  url =  'getShortLink.php?azuid='+azuid+'&url=' + encodeURIComponent(url);

            $.getJSON(url, function(data){

                if( data['status_code'] == 200 ) {
                    var surl = data['surl']; 
                    console.info('shortURL:' + surl);
                    $('.smsm.lnIco .linkBox input').val( surl );
                    $('.smsm.lnIco .linkBox').show();
                }

            });
}

}
</script>
